"""
NVFS core — concrete filesystem implementation.

Modules:
  - superblock  — on-device superblock reader/writer.
  - arena       — arena_* concrete impl (std.storage.arena.Arena).
  - extent      — ExtentMap impl backed by a copy-on-write tree.
  - checkpoint  — checkpoint ring + snapshot family.
  - intent_log  — metadata intent log for crash recovery.
  - encryption  — N6a key hierarchy + AES-GCM envelope (key store, IV derivation).
  - send        — N6b raw send / encrypted replication stream (btrfs-send style).

This module is repo-owned SimpleOS NVFS source migrated from the former
examples project. Hardware backends remain capability-gated; unsupported
optional extensions return FsError.Unsupported instead of placeholder passes.
"""

